dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref>

顺化战役后上任的越南南方共和国司法部长[[張如磉|張如磉]]意識到必须要安抚人民的恐惧，因为“大批的人被处决了”“战斗中的纪律非常地差”“人民知道我们处决了被俘的美国兵以及几个非战斗员的外国人”。<ref>Truong Nhu Trang, A Viet Cong Memoir (1985), p. 153-154</ref>北越第一副總理[[黃晉發|黃晉發]]聲稱屠殺不是北越的命令，而是當地越共指揮官的決定。<ref name="Woodruff2005">{{cite book|author=Mark William Woodruff|title=Unheralded Victory: The Defeat Of The Viet Cong And The North Vietnamese Army, 1961-1973|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=KaootJV5BR4C&pg=PA364|date=October 2005|publisher=Random House Publishing Group|isbn=978-0-89141-866-5|page=364|access-date=2013-12-31|archive-date=2015-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150320005644/http://books.google.com/books?id=KaootJV5BR4C&pg=PA364|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref>

